title: LearnPal MultiSketch Pro 12 [0-day] [NEW]
description:
Don't just say it, display it! Sometimes a thousand words aren't enough to describe what we are trying to communicate to others.
MultiSketch is a versatile whiteboard equipped with many features to help you explain ideas, share your drawings, and collaborate on projects.
Key features: 
Import Sketches (PNG,JPG,PDF)
Export Sketches (PNG,JPG,PDF)
Text Input
Tons of Colours
Share via E-mail, Facebook, Twitter, SMS/MMS
Real-time collaboration with others on your local Wifi Network!

If you like it, Buy it ;-)
